Now I even buy a pair of American fists with the help of someone I trust.
He only gives them to me because he knows I won't give them to him.
The new kids look for weapons in different ways.
Former military man Victor Baranets tried his hand at buying illegal weapons in the mid-1990s when he was preparing to publish an article on the subject.
