We gave him a photo album with "anything we want" in it.
"I thought I was in a high-end store", recalls the soldier.
There is no secret to the buyer, explains Baranets, everything can be tried.
As a potential customer, I don't just buy, we go with the seller into the woods and set up a target.
"They let me shoot and when I'm sure the gun works, we start negotiating", he says.
A shop from her couch
Search engines show the sites and groups on Vkontakte where you can buy weapons "for different purposes".
You don't need any papers or anyone to meet.
"Just have a certain amount of money", says an advertisement on the website "Buy a pistol or a machine gun".
Users leave their requests and ask questions.
And sell to the miners?
"Without a permit, of course", asks the user "Ivan" (spelling retained).
"Buy TT. Moscow", wrote "Fedorenkov" in his very direct request.
The Federal Security Service has a huge network of fake websites and is picking up people who want to buy combat weapons.
